Subject: Re: [T2] engine cutting out problem

In my experience coils will create a miss under load first then get worse.
I would check that the intake system hasn't developed a vacuum leak due to
loose manifold nuts.
I,ve seen it before.
Also check air cleaner.
Good luck.
Brian
72 custom camper
